text: Kujula Kadphises' invasion of Ansi or Kujula Kadphises' invasion of Anxi was an invasion against Indo-Parthia: The Kushans displaced and conquered the regions from the Parthians who retreated to Southern Afghanistan. == References == Category:Pages created with the Article Wizard from 2024 Category:Kushan Empire Category:Wars involving Asia Category:1st-century conflicts
title: Kujula Kadphises' invasion of Anxi
